44
00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:47.107 line:-1 align:center
in your framework or package


45
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:49,042 line:-2
by adding a Documentation
Catalog.


46
00:01:50,444 --> 00:01:52,379 line:-2
