55
00:02:14.067 --> 00:02:15.669 line:-2 align:center
so you can focus on
writing content


56
00:02:15.702 --> 00:02:17.204 line:-1 align:center
with existing markdown syntax


57
00:02:17,237 --> 00:02:18,939 line:-2
you might already be
familiar with.


58
00:02:20,607 --> 00:02:23,877 line:-2
Developer tutorials are centered
around building real projects,


59
00:02:23.911 --> 00:02:25.312 line:-1 align:center
ideally apps.


60
00:02:25.345 --> 00:02:28.182 line:-2 align:center
Tutorial apps should use the API
in your framework


61
00:02:28,215 --> 00:02:29,583 line:-1
in a realistic way.


62
00:02:31.084 --> 00:02:33.887 line:-2 align:center
For example,
in the SwiftUI tutorials,


63
